    <item>
      <title>Text to image synthesis</title>
      <link>https://ysethi92.github.io/project/texttoimage/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Feb 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ysethi92.github.io/project/texttoimage/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;• Implementated a model for synthesizing images for text description using the GAN-CLS algorithm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Implementation is built on top of a DCGAN in PyTorch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• The text descriptions were encoded using the CNN-RNN model and the DCGAN is trained on those text features.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dataset Source: Caltech - UCSD Birds 200-2011&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
